data.description: SELLER WILL ASSIST IN CONTRIBUTING TOWARDS BUYERS  CLOSING COSTS. This traditional home located in the sought out neighborhood of The Ridge at Chukker Creek has curb appeal that captivates at first glance, boasting a stunning blue exterior with Victorian details accentuating the roof and a porch that delivers charm and functionality. A two-car garage stands ready to accommodate vehicles and storage needs. The elegance of wood floors graces the main floor that lead to an open floor plan adorned with coffered ceilings. Natural light dances through the bay window. The kitchen features upgraded cabinets and top-of-the-line appliances. The open layout integrates the kitchen with the living and dining areas, fostering an ease in everyday living. There’s sophistication in every detail, showcased by immaculate ceilings that add an extra touch of grandeur to each room. A dedicated laundry room makes chores convenient. Ascend the staircase adorned by iron balusters to explore the upper floor. The five bedrooms, including 3 smartly appointed bathrooms, offer comfort and privacy.This home invites you to embrace a life of beauty, comfort, and cherished memories!
